high_descs: Go forward and left to the fridge in the corner of the kitchen.
Remove a mango from the bottom shelf of the fridge.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Place the mango into the sink.
Go back to the fridge.
Pick up the mango from the higher shelf of the fridge.
Go back to the sink.
Place the mango into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two mangoes into a SinkBasin.

high_descs: Walk to the fridge on the right.
Pick up the yellow mango from the bottom of the fridge.
Turn around to face the larger sink.
Put the mango in the sink.
Turn to the fridge on the right.
Pick up the mango from the top of the fridge.
Turn around to walk back to the larger sink.
Put the mango with the other fruit in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two mangoes in the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Walk to the fridge in the corner of the kitchen.
Open the fridge and pick up the mango from the bottom shelf.
Turn around and walk to the kitchen sink.
Put the mango into the sink.
Walk back to the fridge.
Open the fridge and pick up the mango from the top shelf.
Turn around and walk to the kitchen sink.
Put the mango into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the two mangoes in the kitchen SinkBasin
